</style>
<html>

<Body>
 
    <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
        <!-- Indicators -->
        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>

        </ol>

        <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="item active">
                <img src="~/Images/Charity1.jpg" alt="Norway" style="width:100%; height:400px" >
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <h1 class="centered">Why only donate money</h1>
                    <h1>when you can do so much more?</h1>

                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="item">
                <img src="~/Images/Charity3.jpg" alt="Norway" style="width:100%; height:400px"/>
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <h1 class="centered">That shirt you no longer need, can help someone else. It’s better to donate than accumulate</h1>
                   
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Left and right controls -->
        <a class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" data-slide="prev">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
        </a>
        <a class="right carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" data-slide="next">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
        </a>
    </div>




    <div class="row">

        <div class="text-center">
            <h1>Charity begins at home but should not end there.</h1>

            <p>At Do your Bit, we believe that charity in any form can be the most self-less thing you can </p>
            <p>do for someone. Deeds of giving are the very foundations of the world. </p>
            <p>You can make the world a better place by getting involved.  </p>
            <p>The change you wish to see in the world! </p>
            <p style="font-size:25px">Do your bit today!</p>
           @*<Button class="btn-success btn-lg">@Html.ActionLink("Donate now!", "Clothm", "Clothes", new { value = "98998", id = "2", @class = "btn btn-success btn-lg" },  null )</Button>*@
            <Button class="btn-secondary btn-lg">@Html.ActionLink("Donate Clothes!", "Clothm", "Clothes", new { value = "98998", id = "2", @class = "btn btn-success btn-lg" },  null )</Button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="vendor/jquery/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="vendor/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</Body>
</html>